        "product_description": {
            "value": "Keep your wetsuit fresh, clean, and long-lasting with the GEAR AID Wetsuit Cleaner and Conditioner Odor Kit. This concentrated shampoo is specially formulated for neoprene, effectively removing salt, chlorine, and residue while eliminating unwanted odors. Simply add to a bin, soak your wetsuit, and let the unscented formula do the work to restore your gear. The 20 fluid ounce concentrated liquid conditions the rubber material to help extend the life and flexibility of your wetsuit, dive boots, gloves, and other neoprene equipment. Ideal for divers, surfers, and water sports enthusiasts, this odor eliminator kit is easy to use and gentle on your gear. Gear up with confidence knowing your wetsuit is clean and ready for your next adventure.",
